column8: Partly cloudy. Slight (20%) chance of rain. The chance of a thunderstorm with little or no rainfall during this afternoon and evening. Light winds.
Mostly sunny morning. Very high (90%) chance of showers in the afternoon and evening. The chance of a thunderstorm in the afternoon and evening. Winds north to northwesterly 25 to 35 km/h.

Cloudy. Very high (90%) chance of showers, most likely in the morning and afternoon. Winds northwest to southwesterly 30 to 35 km/h tending easterly 20 to 25 km/h during the morning then turning north to northeasterly 20 to 30 km/h during the day.

Cloudy. Very high (90%) chance of showers. The chance of a thunderstorm in the afternoon and evening. Winds northwest to northeasterly 30 to 35 km/h tending northwesterly during the afternoon then tending northerly 25 to 30 km/h during the evening.
Cloudy. Very high (90%) chance of showers. The chance of a thunderstorm during the morning. Winds north to northwesterly 25 to 35 km/h turning west to southwesterly 20 to 25 km/h later.
Partly cloudy. Medium (50%) chance of showers. Winds south to southwesterly 25 to 30 km/h turning southeasterly 20 to 25 km/h later.
Partly cloudy. Medium (40%) chance of showers. Winds southeasterly 15 to 25 km/h tending easterly 15 to 20 km/h later.
